title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Tin & Related Articles
description: Imports of Intra EU - Tin & Related Articles in the United Kingdom decreased to 2.47 GBP Million in September from 4.83 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Tin & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 2 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 10.13 GBP Million in March of 2022 and a record low of 0.38 GBP Million in March of 2003. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Tin & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
